hole_acui_min_ctx
-----------------

l1: $ nd _ctx (imp p _wff) $ by imp_intro [#1]

hole_acui_residual_ctx
----------------------

l1: $ nd _ctx (imp p q) $ by imp_intro [#1]

hole_acui_not_chain
-------------------

l1: $ nd _ctx bot $ by not_elim [#1, #2]
l2: $ nd _ctx (neg p) $ by not_intro [l1]
